messages.user_message: My skin feels red and itchy

messages.agent_message: Ok. If you are having trouble breathing, your face is throat is tight, or your face is swelling up, call emergency. Use warm (not hot) water to clean the area (without scrubbing). If this was potentially the result of a product, stop using it immediately. Try a medicated lotion on the area.
